It's just that, Mr. Scott
had requested
a $250,000 withdrawal,

1306
01:19:41,577 --> 01:19:43,279
and apparently in your move
to the Bahamas...

1307
01:19:43,412 --> 01:19:46,415
You tell Mr. Scott,
he'll have his money
in 24 hours.

1308
01:19:46,549 --> 01:19:48,684
Thank you for coming.
Terrific. Mr. Lewis,

1309
01:19:48,818 --> 01:19:50,954
thank you so much
for your time.

1310
01:19:53,589 --> 01:19:55,291
Well, hey, Don,
good to see you.

1311
01:19:55,424 --> 01:19:59,963
Hey, Barry. Well,
Lewis wired me half
my money this morning.

1312
01:20:00,096 --> 01:20:02,098
Half?
Yeah.

1313
01:20:02,231 --> 01:20:06,970
He said that the custodian
of American Investment
didn't put in my paperwork,

1314
01:20:07,103 --> 01:20:09,138
so he sent it
out of his own pocket,

1315
01:20:09,272 --> 01:20:13,376
and he said he'd wire me
the other half very soon.

1316
01:20:13,509 --> 01:20:16,212
You know, Don, I may
have underestimated just how

1317
01:20:16,345 --> 01:20:18,581
strapped for cash
Mr. Lewis is.

1318
01:20:20,583 --> 01:20:24,687
Why would he risk
five million new fresh dollars

1319
01:20:24,820 --> 01:20:27,456
by sending only half
of what he promised
just days ago?

1320
01:20:27,590 --> 01:20:28,858
There's only
one answer to that.

1321
01:20:28,992 --> 01:20:30,693
And that is,
he doesn't have
the full amount,

1322
01:20:30,826 --> 01:20:34,397
and he is much more
cash-strapped
than I first anticipated.

1323
01:20:34,530 --> 01:20:36,365
You're beginning
to worry me, Barry.

1324
01:20:36,499 --> 01:20:40,603
Look, Don, I don't want you
to worry about a thing.
I got this under control.

1325
01:20:40,736 --> 01:20:43,706
Okay? Trust me on this.
It'll be okay.

1326
01:20:43,839 --> 01:20:45,674
I'll take care of it.

1327
01:20:51,314 --> 01:20:52,315
Hello?

1328
01:20:52,448 --> 01:20:54,918
Pastor Minkow, Derek Lewis.

1329
01:20:55,051 --> 01:20:57,520
My understanding was
you were going to deposit
your church money

1330
01:20:57,653 --> 01:21:00,289
two days after Mr. Scott
got his withdrawal fund.

1331
01:21:00,423 --> 01:21:04,894
It's my understanding
that Mr. Scott only received
half of his funds.

1332
01:21:05,028 --> 01:21:06,495
Well, there was a problem
with the paperwork.

1333
01:21:06,629 --> 01:21:08,597
He'll get the balance
tomorrow or the next day.

1334
01:21:08,731 --> 01:21:13,436
Terrific. And once he does,
the church will wire the funds
as I had promised.

1335
01:21:13,569 --> 01:21:16,005
Hey, that's my money.
I control who gets paid
and when.

1336
01:21:16,139 --> 01:21:18,307
No ex-con's gonna
run a number on me.

1337
01:21:18,441 --> 01:21:21,477
You know something,
Mr. Lewis, you're not as smart
as you think you are.

1338
01:21:21,610 --> 01:21:23,112
I know exactly
what you're doing.

1339
01:21:23,246 --> 01:21:26,182
You have no idea what
you're talking about.

1340
01:21:26,315 --> 01:21:29,352
The beauty of grace is that
good people don't go
to heaven,

1341
01:21:29,485 --> 01:21:30,753
forgiven people
go to heaven.

1342
01:21:30,886 --> 01:21:32,655
That's the...
Barry, what is going on?

1343
01:21:32,788 --> 01:21:36,025
Excuse me a second.
Just relax for a minute.
Excuse me.

1344
01:21:36,159 --> 01:21:38,827
Just relax for a minute,
would you, Mike

1345
01:21:38,962 --> 01:21:40,629
I'm gonna punch you
in the face

1346
01:21:40,763 --> 01:21:42,565
the next time
you tell me to relax,
all right?

1347
01:21:42,698 --> 01:21:45,935
Derek Lewis
is suing my uncle
for $10 million,

1348
01:21:46,069 --> 01:21:48,537
for fraud
and misrepresentation.

1349
01:21:48,671 --> 01:21:50,739
Yeah, I know.
He's doing the same thing
to me and the church.

1350
01:21:50,873 --> 01:21:53,242
The cost for the suit
is gonna wipe them out!

1351
01:21:53,376 --> 01:21:56,712
Okay, I need you to stop doing
what you are doing. Okay?

1352
01:21:56,845 --> 01:21:59,382
They've got half their
money back. That's as good
as they're gonna get.

1353
01:21:59,515 --> 01:22:00,349
Just walk away.

1354
01:22:00,483 --> 01:22:02,085
I can't, Mike.

1355
01:22:02,218 --> 01:22:04,887
There's a lot more at stake
than what you're thinking.

1356
01:22:05,021 --> 01:22:07,323
It's gonna be okay.
Just trust me.

1357
01:22:07,456 --> 01:22:09,692
Trust you.
Where have I
heard that before?

1358
01:22:09,825 --> 01:22:12,728
Trusting you
ruined my life, Barry.

1359
01:22:12,861 --> 01:22:16,565
FRANZESE: Barry's intentions
were always good,
at least according to him.

1360
01:22:16,699 --> 01:22:18,734
But he had a lack
of regard for the law

1361
01:22:18,867 --> 01:22:20,869
and eventually,
that became an issue.

1362
01:22:21,004 --> 01:22:23,539
But Barry was
very hard to say no to.

1363
01:22:25,308 --> 01:22:28,177
You don't have to convince me
your intentions are good,
Barry.

1364
01:22:28,311 --> 01:22:32,148
I know you've been
making restitution,
even from prison.

1365
01:22:32,281 --> 01:22:34,950
I owe this community
a lot more than just money,
Michael, you know that.

1366
01:22:35,084 --> 01:22:38,721
Yes, but what you're
asking me to do, I cannot do.

1367
01:22:38,854 --> 01:22:40,589
I might lose my job.

1368
01:22:40,723 --> 01:22:46,195
Look, Michael,
I got Mr. Lewis on tape
saying he has $800 million

1369
01:22:46,329 --> 01:22:49,465
in his accounts at this bank
and if he does,
that's wonderful.

1370
01:22:49,598 --> 01:22:52,068
But if he doesn't,
he's in the process
of destroying

1371
01:22:52,201 --> 01:22:55,071
the lives
of thousands of people
in this community.

1372
01:22:55,204 --> 01:22:57,506
I need your help.
I can't just...

1373
01:22:57,640 --> 01:22:59,642
We can't just
let that happen.

1374
01:22:59,775 --> 01:23:02,911
All I want you to do is
check the balances.

1375
01:23:03,046 --> 01:23:05,214
If they're nowhere
near $800 million,

1376
01:23:05,348 --> 01:23:08,551
then just get out
of that chair,
walk over to that window,

1377
01:23:08,684 --> 01:23:11,454
look outside
and then I'll know for sure.

1378
01:23:11,587 --> 01:23:16,125
All I need are those balances.
Please, Michael,
I'll leave either way.

1379
01:23:16,259 --> 01:23:20,329
All the investment company's
accounts are tied
to this tax ID number.

1380
01:23:24,167 --> 01:23:28,003
You have to help me here.
You have to believe in me.

1381
01:23:28,137 --> 01:23:29,338
Please.

1382
01:23:56,665 --> 01:23:58,801
Man, looks like
it's going to rain.

