01:24:04,340 --> 01:24:07,176
Gamble had me do some
digging the past few days
on my lunch break.

1384
01:24:07,310 --> 01:24:09,078
What's this?

1385
01:24:09,212 --> 01:24:12,315
Articles of incorporation
from a Tijuana company
called Olacane.

1386
01:24:12,448 --> 01:24:13,749
It's Dowry's cash cow.

1387
01:24:15,050 --> 01:24:16,752
They get all their
factoring contracts
from there.

1388
01:24:16,885 --> 01:24:18,621
It's run by some guy
named Oliveros.

1389
01:24:18,754 --> 01:24:20,289
They operate out of
300 square feet

1390
01:24:20,423 --> 01:24:23,058
and share a secretary
with three other businesses.

1391
01:24:23,192 --> 01:24:25,394
The restoration equivalent
of my Ponzi scheme.

1392
01:24:25,528 --> 01:24:30,299
No way that
a 300 square-foot office
in Mexico can substantiate

1393
01:24:30,433 --> 01:24:33,068
hundreds of millions
in factoring business.

1394
01:24:33,202 --> 01:24:35,003
Gamble says,
"Merry Christmas."

1395
01:24:37,606 --> 01:24:38,707
Hello?

1396
01:24:38,841 --> 01:24:40,809
Mr. Lewis,
this is Barry Minkow calling.

1397
01:24:40,943 --> 01:24:42,044
How'd you get this number?

1398
01:24:42,178 --> 01:24:43,646
You have your spies.
I have mine.

1399
01:24:43,779 --> 01:24:45,214
What do you want?

1400
01:24:45,348 --> 01:24:46,849
I'd like to meet you in
Los Angeles tomorrow

1401
01:24:46,982 --> 01:24:49,185
and I'd like you to bring
the rest of Don Scott's money.

1402
01:24:49,318 --> 01:24:50,219
You gotta be joking.

1403
01:24:50,353 --> 01:24:52,121
5:00 p.m., LA Resort Hotel.

1404
01:24:52,255 --> 01:24:54,757
Unless of course
you'd like me to take
the information I've obtained

1405
01:24:54,890 --> 01:24:56,659
and turn it over to the FBI
or the Journal.

1406
01:24:56,792 --> 01:24:58,361
And what do you have
on me, Mr. Minkow?

1407
01:24:58,494 --> 01:25:01,330
There's only $387,000
in your bank accounts

1408
01:25:01,464 --> 01:25:03,399
instead of the $800 million
that you purport to have.

1409
01:25:03,532 --> 01:25:04,833
You just wait a minute.

1410
01:25:04,967 --> 01:25:06,935
You, Mr. Lewis,
are running a Ponzi scheme.

1411
01:25:07,069 --> 01:25:09,472
No, you're the ex-con.
You're running the scam.

1412
01:25:09,605 --> 01:25:10,806
I'm doing the work of God.

1413
01:25:10,939 --> 01:25:11,907
Hey, I said wait a minute.

1414
01:25:12,040 --> 01:25:13,442
Protecting the weak.

1415
01:25:13,576 --> 01:25:17,280
I'll see you tomorrow,
LA Resort Hotel, 5:00 p.m.

1416
01:25:17,413 --> 01:25:19,047
Good night, Mr. Lewis.

1417
01:25:28,924 --> 01:25:31,227
Lisa, I wanted
to tell you something,

1418
01:25:31,360 --> 01:25:34,363
but I wanted to make sure
that it came out right.

1419
01:25:34,497 --> 01:25:35,798
So I wanted to be careful.

1420
01:25:35,931 --> 01:25:41,204
Barry, for once in your life,
don't speak, okay?

1421
01:25:43,806 --> 01:25:45,974
Look, I just
want to say that

1422
01:25:47,510 --> 01:25:51,347
I see the people
who always second-guess
your motives.

1423
01:25:51,480 --> 01:25:55,518
I see them. I see the people
who always raise an eyebrow.

1424
01:25:55,651 --> 01:25:57,986
And I know that
you struggle, okay?

1425
01:25:59,955 --> 01:26:01,457
I know that you
struggle knowing that

1426
01:26:01,590 --> 01:26:05,127
