will never trust a word
that you say.

1427
01:26:08,130 --> 01:26:10,065
I mean, 'cause
let's be real, Barry,

1428
01:26:10,199 --> 01:26:13,202
most people will walk away,
most people are going to
just shake their heads

1429
01:26:13,336 --> 01:26:16,205
and steer clear of you
and think that
you're a con forever.

1430
01:26:19,875 --> 01:26:22,478
But that's not me.

1431
01:26:22,611 --> 01:26:26,382
I appreciate that
more then you'll ever know.

1432
01:26:26,515 --> 01:26:31,920
I got nothing to offer you
but a $26 million
restitution order

1433
01:26:32,054 --> 01:26:34,790
and suspicious glares
and grins every time

1434
01:26:34,923 --> 01:26:38,561
I walk by with you
in some public arena.

1435
01:26:38,694 --> 01:26:40,296
But I will tell you this,

1436
01:26:42,298 --> 01:26:47,536
if I had to serve
eight Super Bowls
in prison again,

1437
01:26:47,670 --> 01:26:50,539
and knew that
you'd be waiting for me
when I got out,

1438
01:26:52,841 --> 01:26:54,910
I would go
right back to prison.

